strings.Value: {n}Nok-Nok's ears perk up as you approach. He looks dirty, and his clothes are in greater disarray than normal. His eyes are also a strange, clear blue, like marbles.{/n} "There you are, taking your time!"

"Met foul-smelling plant woman with ears. Tried kill me, but Nok-Nok bravely cowered on floor and held breath." {n}He puffs up proudly.{/n} "Old trick, from way back in tribe. Make them think Nok-Nok already dead before they kick and hit more." {n}Nok-Nok frowns.{/n} "Except this time, trick worked."

"Foul-smelling plant woman with ears no keep kicking or hitting me, and her spell..." {n}Nok-Nok swallows, lifting the rags from his side to reveal a huge, black scorch mark cutting close to his ribs.{/n} "Dodge most of it. Made eyes all funny, though." {n}He blinks, and some of the red returns... but slowly.{/n} "Starting see normal again, almost good as new."

"Ready to stab! Point the way, and knife will follow." {n}Nok-Nok grins.{/n} "Plus, now you here. Let's play same game with her, except this time, Nok-Nok has clever plan... keep kicking her when she falls, and make sure she not do same death fake trick Nok-Nok do!"
